Package org.neo4j.cypher.internal.javacompat

Class ExecutionEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.cypher.internal.javacompat.ExecutionEngine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QueryExecutionEngine
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SnapshotExecutionEngine, SystemExecutionEngine
    public class ExecutionEngine
extends Object
implements QueryExecutionEngine
    To run a Cypher query, use this class. This class construct and initialize both the cypher compiler and the cypher runtime, which is a very expensive operation so please make sure this will be constructed only once and properly reused.
